rComments: Professor MacIntosh could put more effort into making his lectures more interesting, he never seems too excited to be teaching. Expects a lot of details and insight for his papers, but also doesn’t allow for more than three pages. Thank god for the group project, although good luck if you have a bad group as the group project is worth 40%.

Course with MacIntosh is awful! He is extremely boring! If it's optional for you stay away. By the end of the semester I will have written 2 exams, 9 papers (one 30 pages long), done a 30 minute presentation, and done a big assignment that requires collecting a month worth of receipts. Way too much work to be done. Don't have that much time!
E-Mac was alright, but could be really boring. Can come off a bit mean and arrogant, but he's actually a nice guy.
